original: Åhmansson, Nils Carl Erik, assu-ransdirektör, Göteborg, f. 20/12/97 i Gbg av dir. Nils E. Ä. o. Anna Larsson. G. 34 m. Ingeborg Wulff. Barn: Gunvor f. 35, Ingela 36, Nils Erik 41. —• Verkst. dir. i Sv:es ångf. assur, fören. 43, i Ömises. Förs :bol. Protec-tion & Indemnity fr. 46. Led. av krigs-försäkr md 43, styr :led. i Lloyds’ Reg. sv. komm.. fr. 43, i A-B Gbgs Hand:-bank 46. RVO, FFrK.
translated: Åhmansson, Nils Carl Erik, insurance director, Gothenburg, b. 20/12/97 in Gothenburg, son of director Nils E. Ä. and Anna Larsson. Married in 1934 to Ingeborg Wulff. Children: Gunvor b. 1935, Ingela b. 1936, Nils Erik b. 1941. Managing director of Swedish Steamship Insurance Association from 1943, of Ömises Insurance Company from 1946. Member of the War Insurance Committee from 1943, board member of Lloyds' Register Swedish committee from 1943, and of A-B Gothenburgs Handelsbank from 1946. Recipient of the Royal Order of Vasa and the Freemason's Order of the Sword.
